Why choose Magnitude Finance?

Our PCP and HP options are compared throughout our extensive panel of lenders, so you know you’re getting the best deal available. Whether you’re looking to fund a daily driver or a supercar, we have multiple options available to get you into your new car at a figure that’s right for you.

We always give customers the best options we have available, with competitive rates to help save them money. As a finance broker, we work directly with the finance companies on our panel, which means we can get you access to more competitive rates than most dealers, so over the course of the agreement we could help you save money for something special.

WHAT FINANCE OPTIONS ARE AVAILABLE?

Whether it be daily drivers, family cars, business cars, supercars, collectables, or classics, our car finance packages can be tailored to meet the expectations and exact requirements of our clients.

We offer PCP and Hire Purchase via our online calculator, giving you the ease of applying quickly and easily online. Lease Purchase, and Balanced Payments options are also available via our award winning team, for those looking for something a little more specialist.

We also offer finance solutions for Motorhomes, Horseboxes, LCVs and many more lifestyle and leisure vehicles.

So, how do I get a quote?

Our online finance calculator and online dashboard give you the tools to get car finance quotes in just a few taps. Just add the car, pop in a few details and that’s it, you will have accurate PCP and HP car finance quotes in no time!

Once you have your quote, you can apply online, Our application process only takes a couple of minutes, and then your dedicated finance specialist will be in touch when we have an update regarding your acceptance.

We can introduce you to a limited number of lenders that offer finance products, but we do not offer any advice or recommendations. We do not charge you a fee for our services, but we receive commission from the lenders we introduce you to. The commission we receive is either a fixed fee or a percentage of the amount you borrow. The commission we receive varies depending on how you are introduced to us, which lender we place you with, and which finance product you choose. We will likely pass a proportion of the commission we receive to the motor retailer that introduced you to us. The commission we receive and pay will not affect the amount of interest you pay under your credit agreement, when compared to customers in circumstances similar to you.

We will always introduce you to the lender that provides products for your needs, at the interest rate suitable for your credit profile. If you ask us, we will tell you the amount of commission we are paid for introducing you to the finance lender. We may select a lender which is part of our group (Unity Auto Finance Ltd). We will only ever select this particular lender from the panel available to us if it is in your interests and is the most appropriate lender for your particular needs.
